<data name="FaqTitle" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>&lt;span&gt;Frequently Asked&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Questions&lt;/strong&gt;</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqDescription" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>You can find answers here to frequently asked questions about services and workflow. For detailed information or special offers, you can always contact me.</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqQuestion-1" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Which technologies and languages are used in projects?</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqAnswer-1" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>The most up-to-date technologies are used based on scalability and performance. On the backend, .NET Core and Node.js architectures; on the frontend, React and Angular; and for AI integrations, PyTorch and TensorFlow libraries are adopted as standards.</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqQuestion-2" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>How does your project development and delivery process work?</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqAnswer-2" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Processes are managed with the principle of transparency and predictability. A roadmap consisting of Analysis, Design, Development and Testing phases is followed. Regular reporting is provided at every stage to ensure the final product fully meets the requirements.</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqQuestion-3" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Is technical support and maintenance available after project delivery?</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqAnswer-3" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Yes, sustainability of developed systems is essential. In addition to the post-delivery warranty period; maintenance and support services are provided to keep the system up-to-date, apply security patches and add new features.</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqQuestion-4" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Can the developed software integrate with existing systems?</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqAnswer-4" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Yes, the developed solutions have a modular structure. Through API (Application Programming Interface) technologies and custom middleware software, full integrations can be achieved with the company's existing ERP, CRM or accounting systems.</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqQuestion-5" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Do you provide technical consultancy services besides software development?</value>
</data>
<data name="FaqAnswer-5" xml:space="preserve">
  <value>Not only coding, but also strategic planning support is provided. Professional consultancy services are offered in system analysis, AI adaptation strategies, database optimization and software architecture.</value>
</data>
